{"tid":239522,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"金庸撚(邊個女角最好打）","createTime":"2017-05-11T17:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T16:51:47.000Z","uid":22645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6cb31fba09a1d0698ace9fa21002f584f3a8d8","tid":239522,"uid":22645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"成日見到連登有開金庸嘅post，睇到好多師兄都好有心得，我小學開始第一次睇金庸嘅書，當時唔知好多位都睇唔明，但係幾乎每年都會翻睇，愈嚟愈鍾意。<br />\n近排TVB播射鵰，咁我頭先食晚飯突然問老豆「喂，你覺得黃蓉好打定係小龍女好打？」<br />\n老豆：「小龍女啦，陳玉蓮好乸堅。」<br />\n我（配合佢年齡mode）：「但係翁美玲識打狗棒又識九陰真經喎。」<br />\n老豆：「黃蓉神鵰個時好廢。」<br />\n我：「有左呀嘛。」<br />\n大家覺得金庸入面邊D女角色好打？今次唔好講男人！！！！"},{"pid":"535e1a871a750cb4246f8e04d3d2a79d292c38cd","tid":239522,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"梅超風算唔算勁"},{"pid":"787539a9165d3de402048ab8618b8ff6462abadc","tid":239522,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"越女劍<br />\n完"},{"pid":"bb44eb72a1ca16375ef25cb2b35e1c3b924b2d06","tid":239522,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"東方不敗"},{"pid":"85cd2e63c93367908878c0b8c57561aaa9291475","tid":239522,"uid":22645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東方不敗</blockquote><br />\n係女人咩？！？！"},{"pid":"15ae79472ccf6e25bd13bea05ed21f0cd1dce8b5","tid":239522,"uid":22645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越女劍<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁快完我啦"},{"pid":"92443c02c2a60d3a842e1a39af9dc53953e40276","tid":239522,"uid":22645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梅超風算唔算勁</blockquote><br />\n應該算係幾勁，但我覺得林朝英呀，天山童姥個D勁好多"},{"pid":"ff4d20cc87995bb9959dcd6cc55e55c65243e4fc","tid":239522,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東方