c=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2041cdbe331bc6eeddbcb9bcd66a28d3a847d9","tid":239522,"uid":8657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T22:47:53.000Z","msg":"　　八十名越國劍士沒學到阿青的一招劍法，但他們已親眼見到了神劍的影子。每個人都知道了，世間確有這樣神奇的劍法。八十個人將一絲一忽勉強捉摸到的劍法影子傳授給了旁人，單是這一絲一忽的神劍影子，越國吳士的劍法便已無敵於天下。 <br />\n有咩劍法望兩眼咩都學唔到，但係拎黎教人都可以無敵天下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0625f085f035fcc2e85d9f3b0e771bfedcc7de06","tid":239522,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T22:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>越女劍<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁快完我啦</blockquote><br />\n完"},{"pid":"c5b21380f34cb5a74f0389c9f37fb7ee2ea2d700","tid":239522,"uid":13628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T22:54:03.000Z","msg":"睇錯 邊個女角最好丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153bd10dfd8d8637446269ff1e5cb49e8e636b39","tid":239522,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:12:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6df3d73a64bf72afb8c42c010a165d9a951e3a3","tid":239522,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯 邊個女角最好丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又另一個講唔完嘅新 post"},{"pid":"64960de60a5060ad7884e52e798abbe20e2467bd","tid":239522,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:13:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3067d815596dd896c536031e556effff28b3fd2","tid":239522,"uid":55463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T23:17:59.000Z","msg":"蕭清慧